hes long and 40 inches wide. The track includes eight curved pieces, one straight piece and one terminal piece where the power source connects. This LionChief train sets run on a set amount of power, 18 volts. Other train sets vary in the amount of power sent to the track; for instance, turning up the speed of a train increases the power sent to the train. In these cases, features, such as the smoke stack or the headlight, will not work as well when the power is decreased. However, since the LionChief has a set amount of power flowing through the track at all times, the headlight, sounds and smokestack work just as well at low speeds as they would at high speeds.","One of the special features about Lionel LionChief train sets is that you can operate multiple LionChief trains on a single track. LionChief pairs each remote to the locomotive, so you can put two trains on a single track and operate them separately with two remotes."]},"id":"ddb88814-7163-4002-b7fc-0625cce5c062","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Assembly"},"id":"5f9f81a0-4c29-414d-8b4c-ad8359aa1d5f","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/6PGnhjWCnwg6kyc2vPjFzj.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"Lionel LionChief train sets do not come with additional accessories, such as signs or figurines, like many other train sets do. Additional road signage and figurines make it so you can create scenery for your model train. It is disappointing that Lionel doesn’t include more with this train set.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/57213-lionel-the-scout5.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/6PGnhjWCnwg6kyc2vPjFzj.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"6PGnhjWCnwg6kyc2vPjFzj","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/6PGnhjWCnwg6kyc2vPjFzj.jpg","alt":""},"id":"e694efa1-7838-4638-a857-b31c147303f2","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The remote control that comes with the Scout not only operates the speed and direction of the train, but also the bell, whistle and announcement. The remote control takes three AAA batteries to operate, and batteries are not included with your purchase. A tiny screw seals the cover to the batteries, and it is a nuisance to get the screw out to insert or replace batteries. This seems to be the case with LionChief remotes."]},"id":"cd4e14d6-70e9-4bb2-a476-f43e8895dac7","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Functionality"},"id":"18544aa1-561b-4e59-820c-9ba52b616fce","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Lionel representatives were kind and helpful when they answered questions we asked during our research. They are available via phone and email. There is also a downloadable manual on the website if you lose the one it comes with. The Scout Steam Set is covered by a one-year warranty."]},"id":"49d02f74-3c32-465e-95ad-57724c4b15a0","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"9968cb01-ba46-477e-96bb-01f21440595e","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The LionChief Scout Steam Set is one of the most impressive model train sets we reviewed. The locomotive has a sturdy build, and all of the train cars promote fine detail that will make model enthusiasts happy. Although there was a paint smudge on the conductor in the model we received, we believe that overall quality is top-notch when it comes this train set."]},"id":"492d26eb-da7b-44c5-9364-85a8c4d9d375","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_57241","url":"/lionel-the-scout-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"anna-burleson","url":"/author/anna-burleson","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Anna Burleson","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"4bFWMi8qjrUwQuwAFnJjZM","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2013-08-13T13:44:33Z","datePublished":"2013-08-13T13:44:33Z","name":"Lionel 2-4-2 LionChief Scout Steam Set","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued.","re